            "class": "",
            "text": "An utterly false rendering. Rightly as Rev., of an eternal sin. So Wyc., everlasting trespass. The A. V. has gone wrong in following Tyndale, who, in turn, followed the erroneous text of Erasmus, κρίσεως, judgment, wrongly rendered damnation. See ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Matthew 23:33",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ", and compare Rev. there. ",
